name: Air Handling Units, Heat Exchange
leaf_category: Air Handling Units For Air Handling Units
description: We Offer Customized Air Handling Units Comprising Of A Combination Of One Or More Sections from available range, viz. Fan Section, Chilled Water Coil Section, Heating Coil Section, Filtration Sections, Face/Bypass damper Sections, Mixing Section, Humidification Section, etc

name: Air Terminal Devices, Colour-White
leaf_category: Air Terminal Devices For Air Handling Units
description: Our Terminal Devices Are Designed To Ensure A Long Trouble Free But Satisfactory Operation and can be offered in GI, Aluminium and SS construction except for jet (diffuser) nozzles which is available in Aluminium construction only.

name: Air Washer Units, Cooling Device
leaf_category: Air Washer Units For Air Handling Units
description: The Evaporative Air Cooling Process Is An Adiabatic Process Where The outlet air conditions are entirely dependent on the inlet air conditions without addition or removal of energy from the air stream.

name: Tube Axial Fans, Angle-Fixed & Variable
leaf_category: Tube Axial Fans For Air Handling Units
description: Use Of Fixed Angle Blades And Variable Angle Blades, We Also Offer Flexibility In Fan Selection Over A Wide range of duty static pressures. The axial impellers can be provided in short casing models for wall mounting or long casing models for duct inline applications

name: Bag Filters And Cyclones, Dust Collection
leaf_category: Bag Filters And Cyclones For Air Handling Units
description: While The Cyclone Initiates The Dust Separation Process, Final Dust Separation And Collection For A Variety of industrial applications can be achieved by use of bag filters.

name: Air Locks, Rotary Air Lock
leaf_category: Air Locks For Air Handling Units
description: Rotary Air Locks In Cast Body With Shaft MOC In MS And SS Options

name: Dampers, Flow Control Of Air
description: Damper A Mechanical Device In A Duct Or Chimney That Regulates Airflow. We Can provide parallel blade low leakage MS or Aluminium dampers for ON & OFF application, which may be used for occasional isolation of one line from another

name: Louvers, Aluminium And Stainless Steel
description: A Stream Of Air Moving Across The Louver Is Forced To Turn At Steep Vertical Angles in an upward direction, thereby allowing bigger dust particles to separate and deposit at louver entry.

name: Roof Extractors, Protection-Rain
leaf_category: Roof Extractors For Air Handling Units
description: Roof Extractors Comprises Of A Tube Axial Fan,Suitably Modified To Accomodate Rain Protection Hood and provided with fixing arrangement for roof mounting

name: Centrifugal Fans, WC Pressure-1500MM
leaf_category: Centrifugal Fans For Air Handling Units
description: Centrifugal Fans Range Of Ventilation Fans And Upto 1500mm WC Pressures Of Industrial Application Fans Which Are Suitable For Both Clean air applications, as well as, dust laden air.

name: Air Filters, Ventilation And Air Conditioning
leaf_category: Air Filters For Air Handling Units
description: Air Filtering Media Consists Of Suitable Fibrous Materials Which Are Designed To Remove solid particulatessuch as dust, pollen, mold, and bacteria from the air.
